<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pistol Shot - Weapon Details</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .weapon-profile {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .weapon-images {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .weapon-image {
            max-width: 200px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .weapon-info {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .upgrade-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .upgrade-table th, .upgrade-table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .upgrade-table th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #063f5c;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <main>
        <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; color: #063f5c;">Pistol Shot</h1>

        <div class="weapon-profile">
            <div class="weapon-images">
                <img src="/images/weapons/pistol-shot.png" alt="Pistol Shot" class="weapon-image">
                <img src="/images/weapons/pistol-shot-upgrade.png" alt="Pistol Shot Upgraded" class="weapon-image">
            </div>
            <div class="weapon-info">
                <h2>Weapon of Amelia Watson</h2>
                <p>The Pistol Shot is Amelia's primary weapon, known for its rapid fire and precision. It evolves into a more powerful form with upgrades, increasing its damage and capabilities.</p>
            </div>
            <h2>Upgrade Path</h2>
            <table class="upgrade-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Level</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 1</td>
                    <td>Shoots 3 Projectiles forward.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 2</td>
                    <td>Shoot 2 additional shots, and each bullet can pierce +1 times.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 3</td>
                    <td>Increase damage by 20%.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 4</td>
                    <td>Bullets ricochet if hit limit is reached.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 5</td>
                    <td>Each bullet can pierce +1 times. Reduce the time between attacks by 25%.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 6</td>
                    <td>Increase damage by 20%.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Level 7</td>
                    <td>For the next 2 seconds, 15% of all damage taken by target is stored in time. Then target takes total of stored damage.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
